script.name: plugin.guilds.infomenu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds' $guild = get global variable: name='menu.guild' $guild.data = get global variable: name='guilds.data'
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] $guild = $a.data set global variable: name='menu.guild' value=$a.data gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Returned] set global variable: name='menu.guild' value=null end
return null
sub.BuildMenu: $tGuild = $guild.data[$guild]
$menu = create custom menu array
$text = $tGuild['desc'] if $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text end
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=107 add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$read.text
if $tGuild['member'] $guild.level = $tGuild['level'] $text = $tGuild['ranks'][$guild.level] if is datatype[ $text ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $x = $text[0] $y = $text[1] $text = read text: page=$x id=$y else $text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=112 $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text $text = create custom menu string notoriety bar: level=$guild.level, show empty=[FALSE] $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text $text.cols = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=113 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text
$guild.xp = $tGuild['exp'] @ $max.xp = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.utils : type='getXP' Value1=$guild.level Value 2=null $percent = fixed multiply and divide: $guild.xp * 100 / $max.xp $text = create custom menu string progress: width=100 progress=$percent% $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols
else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=108 add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text end
$text = $tGuild['founder'] if $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=118 add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$read.text
$text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=119 $text = create text for custom menu, left=$read.text, right=$text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text end
$text = $tGuild['backstory'] if $text if $tGuild['founder'] add info line section to menu: $menu else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=118 add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$read.text end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$read.text end
$text = $tGuild['hq']['obj'] if $text -> exists $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104319 add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$read.text $sector = $text -> get sector $text = $text -> get name $text = create text for custom menu, left=$text, right=$sector add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text end
$aRanks = $tGuild['ranks'] if $aRanks $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=114 add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$read.text $i = 1 while $i <= 10 $text = $aRanks[$i] $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text $text = sprintf: fmt='%s. %s', $i, $read.text, null, null, null if $i == $guild.level $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=[MenuColour.Green] text=$text else $text = create custom menu column string, position=20 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text end add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text inc $i = end end
set menu option: $menu, icon=29 set menu option: $menu, no select lines=[TRUE] $text = $tGuild['backstory'] if $text if read text: page id=$page.id, id=$text exists set menu option: $menu, voiced description page=$page.id, id=$text end end
$text = $tGuild['name'] $text = read text: page=$page.id id=$text $player.name = get player name $input = create input: id='guild.info' menu=$menu title=$text description=$player.name callback=null endsub return null
